14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 1, Chapter 331, O.S.L.
16 2022 (59 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 1151.30), is amended to read as
17 follows:
18 Section 1151.30. A. A residential or commercial roofing
19 contractor providing repairs or improvement services to be paid by
20 an insured from the proceeds of a property or casualty insurance
21 policy shall not, as an inducement to the sale or provision of goods
22 or services to an insured, advertise or promise to pay, directly or
23 indirectly, all or part of any applicable insurance deductible or
24 offer to compensate an insured for providing any service to the
